        "reviews-list": {
          "type": "t_testimonials",
          "static": true,
          "settings": {},
          "blocks": {
            "t_testimonial_NDLwEM": {
              "type": "t_testimonial",
              "name": "Testimonial",
              "settings": {
                "image": "shopify://shop_images/Figure.png",
                "name": "ColdFireChief",
                "paragraph": "<p>Very good product. It took half the time shaving the dogs than it did with a shaver at 3x the price. It's chargeable, but doesnt charge super fast (about 50-60 minutes to charge it fully, about 25-ish%). It is quieter than most shavers but seemed to get louder when a guard was attached to it. </p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "t_testimonial_njDKdH": {
              "type": "t_testimonial",
              "name": "Testimonial",
              "settings": {
                "image": "shopify://shop_images/Figure_1.png",
                "name": "Carla Farias",
                "paragraph": "<p>This product worked wonders. My girly pal is a golden doodle and had a long winter and she was in bad shape. These grooming kit was definitely much quieter than others I’ve purchased. Priced pretty well and they do not disappoint. For the price point, it’s a must buy.</p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "t_testimonial_AnwqJg": {
              "type": "t_testimonial",
              "name": "Testimonial",
              "settings": {
                "image": "shopify://shop_images/Figure_2.png",
                "name": "Laura Martinez",
                "paragraph": "<p>Very low noise level. Since it’s cordless, it’s easy to use. Cuts my schnauzer’s hair to the exact length I want. Blades are sharp and produces a smooth and even finish.</p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "t_testimonial_3rGJDr": {
              "type": "t_testimonial",
              "name": "Testimonial",
              "settings": {
                "image": "shopify://shop_images/Figure_3.png",
                "name": "Jessica Brown",
                "paragraph": "<p>I cannot say enough good things about these clippers, they are AMAZING! The battery life is impressive, the blades stay sharp, the cuts are clean, and they don’t get hot even during longer grooming sessions. The low noise level is a huge win for our nervous dogs; they tolerate these so much better than louder clippers we’ve tried.</p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            },
            "t_testimonial_3LXJwa": {
              "type": "t_testimonial",
              "name": "Testimonial",
              "settings": {
                "image": "shopify://shop_images/Figure_4.png",
                "name": "Rachel Wilson",
                "paragraph": "<p>\"This is a must have for any parent. It looks nice, super<br/>functional, sleek, literally anything you would want in a<br/>stroller. Currently purchasing my second one.\"</p>"
              },
              "blocks": {}
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
